title: A Fabulous Day In NYC
desc: NYC get ready, Its the time of the year when 3 of NYC's Top Promoters Shut Down The City #AFabulousDay In NYC at Orbit NYC Doors open from 6-12 Huge birthday celebration for promoters @Chad_BCE, @RobMCH & @Duvey1 This is A Sold Out Event Every Year Music by #Power105 own Dj Sussone & Dj Will, alongside Dj TrueBlends, Dj Kyndal Marie & Dj Legend ?To celebrate your birthday or inquire about bottle service email chad.bce.events@gmail.com
